Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:22.71,EN LYRICS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But the words you said were they true
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:26.01,EN LYRICS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Or just selfish lies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:28.88,EN LYRICS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}After all of this you put me through
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:32.16,EN LYRICS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't even know myself
