Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:44.52,EN LYRICS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Don't know why, what did I do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.52,EN LYRICS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Gave all I ever had
