Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.64,EN LYRICS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Clinging to the past
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.67,EN LYRICS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Tried to make it last, but I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:21:01.21,EN LYRICS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All I know is gone, all I know is gone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:07.59,EN LYRICS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All I know is gone, now I'm all alone
